{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We must have had some clothing when we went into the shower room, because we got undressed in the shower room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is where we left the clothing on the side of the shower room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I took out my ID card, took it with me to the shower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I ripped it up into these tiny, tiny, little pieces.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I let it down, into the drain, with the water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was the end of the forged identity.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And eventually, after two minutes or so, they run you out, or they run you out of the shower room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was another barrack that you had to run through, naked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And some people were throwing some clothing articles at you, which were totally, I mean, out of place and out of size.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And most of these things had a lot of paint.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were painted over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If you ever-- if you ever escape from a camp, you could be easily recognized by the red paint on your clothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, oil paint, dried oil paint, stripes on your back or crosses or whatever else, all kinds of forms that they painted.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But usually-- it was a-- it was a horrible feeling to wear a jacket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It sort of weighed you down, the dry paint.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I mean it was awful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And these are the things you wind up with and a pair of clogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And luckily I-- and, of course, they run you outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You are still wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You know, you must realized, there are no towels to get dry or anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You come out of the shower, wet, and you have a bundle of those rags in your arms.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they run you outside in the snow, ice.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
